WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
OneCommit dashboard — creating your athlete profile with times, GPA, and preferences.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:12.000
Smart school matching — browsing Reach, Target, and Foundational tiers with match percentages.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:20.000
SmartAdd search — typing preferences to discover matched schools and adding them to your dashboard.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Generating a personalized outreach email to a college coach, ready to send from your own inbox.

00:00:30.000 --> 00:00:40.000
Reply tracking dashboard — seeing which coaches have responded and managing follow-ups.

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:50.000
Outreach dashboard — tracking sent messages, open rates, and engagement across all your schools.
